storage format:
    game.db                 sprite descriptor and sprite graph
    game.assets/bg.png      background
    game.assets/*.png       sprites

general:
    a state runs on a 250 clock

bg.png:
    400x400 pixels

game.db:
.sprite
<id>
<image name>
<x y coordinates>

.state
<id>
<on clock actions>

EXAMPLE FILE
============

// this is not final and contains bugs ; work in progress

.sprite
1
player_left.png

.sprite
2
player_right.png

.sprite
10
player_bullet_left.png
.sprite
11
player_bullet_left_2.png

.sprite
